column1: Between 1 July 2019 and 30 June 2020, will an armed group from Yemen engage in a campaign that systematically kills 1,000 or more civilians in Yemen?

column6: It is difficult to get exact number of kills from that area. However answer to this question has become slightly simpler as it considers a larger number. So, I don't believe 1,000+ kills will take place.
